
using python3.10
Firstly insert open ai key in myapp/views.py file.
install requirement file.
using pip3 install -r requirement.txt

run the server using this command:-
    python3 manage.py runserver


hit this url only once for creating index:-
    https://127.0.0.1:8000/create_data

you will be redirect to https://127.0.0.1:8000 url after index creating.

Now you can test the chatbot on this link https://127.0.0.1:8000.

when you want to clear the chat just click on clear chat button.